f> Historically, the suburb was home to [[Awan (tribe)|Malik]] and [[chudhary(Pakistan)|chudhary]] tribesmen, but recently has seen a growth in farmhouses of the rich and wealthy from nearby [[Islamabad]], including that of [[Pervez Musharraf]], [[Makhdoom]] [[Ameen Faheem]] and Dr Tariq Fazal Chaudry. The famous political leader & cricketer [[Imran khan]] also lives nearby. The private housing society of [[Malik Riaz]], Bahria Enclave Islamabad, is just 4km away from Chakshahzad. [[Zero point interchange]] (the centre of the city) is just 12km away.And also near Chatta '''Bakhtawar''' village,near ''ParkView Town''' ''''' and famous '''Punjab cash and Carry''',In the Near foreign visa services provide '''Garry,''In the behind '''Green Avenue''' and '''Park Enclave''' The famous anchor Javed Chaudry also lives in Shehzad town, Chakshahzad. It is also considered as a home for some important landmarks including National Agricultural Research Center, Health Services Academy (HSA),Abasyn University Islamabad Campus and COMSATS University. <ref>[https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/revealed-musharrafs-luxury-retirement-pad-900652.html Revealed: Musharraf's luxury retirement pad - Asia - World - The Independent<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Neighbourhoods of Islamabad}}\n\n[[Category:Union councils of Islamabad Capital Territory]]\n[[Category:Villages in Islamabad Capital Territory]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Islamabad Capital Territory]]\n\n{{Pakistan-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| official_name           =  Chak Shahzad\n| name                    =  \n| settlement_type         =  Suburb\n| image_skyline           =  \n| imagesize               =  240px\n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_map               = \n| mapsize                 = 150 px\n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| coordinates             = {{coord|33.662|73.143|region: