 {{flagicon|POL}}\n|score=0\u20131\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1986/matches/round=17/match=4117/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report]\n|team2={{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|location=[[Warzow]]\n|stadium=\n|attendance=100,000\n|referee={{flagicon|SCO}}[[Bob Valentine (referee)|Bob Valentine]] \n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=9 November 1988\n|time=\n|team1=[[Real Madrid]] {{flagicon|ESP}}\n|score=3\u20132\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1986/matches/round=17/match=4118/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report]\n|team2={{flagicon|POL}} [[G\u00f3rnik Zabrze]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|location=[[Madrid]]\n|stadium=[[Estadio Santiago Bernabeu]] \n|attendance=62,000\n|referee={{flagicon|FRG}}[[Dieter Pauly]]\n|result=W\n}}\n\n====Quarterfinals====\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=28 February 1989\n|time=17:30\n|team1=[[PSV Eindhoven]] {{flagicon|NED}}\n|score=1\u20131\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1986/matches/round=18/match=4137/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report]\n|team2={{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]]\n|goals1=[[Bo\u0161ko \u01f4urovski|\u01f4urovski]] {{goal|7}}<br />[[\u017darko \u0110urovi\u0107|\u0110urovi\u0107]] {{goal|12}}<br />[[Borislav Cvetkovi\u0107|Cvetkovi\u0107]] {{goal|39}}<br />[[Milan Jankovi\u0107 (footballer, born 1959)|Jankovi\u0107]] {{goal|84|pen.}}<br>Krivokapic{{yel|88}} \n|goals2=[[Hugo S\u00e1nchez]] {{goal|66}}<br>[[Hugo Sanchez]]{{goal|87|pen}}<br>Salguero{{yel|53}}\n|location=[[Eindhoven]]\n|stadium=[[Philips Stadion]]\n|attendance=90,000\n|referee={{flagicon|ENG}}[[Keith Hackett]] \n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=14 March 1989\n|time=20:00\n|team1=[[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]] {{flagicon|ESP}}\n|score=2\u20131\n|aet=yes\n|aggregatescore=3-2\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1986/matches/round=18/match=4138/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report]\n|team2={{flagicon|NED}} [