ive Stars: Missouri's Most Famous Generals |publisher=University of Missouri Press |location=Columbia, Missouri |year=2006 |page=74 |isbn=978-0-8262-1656-4 |oclc=191943891 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=PKvpsMbH5goC&pg=PA74&lpg=PA74&dq=Columbus+Delano+Grant+Scandal&q=Columbus%20Delano%20Grant%20Scandal |accessdate=January 30, 2010}}\n*{{cite book |last=Nevins |first=Allan |authorlink=Allan Nevins |title=Hamilton Fish: The Inner History of the Grant Administration |url=https://www.questia.com/PM.qst?a=o&d=94934148 |accessdate=April 11, 2010 |year=1937 |publisher=Macmillan|location=New York City |isbn=978-0-8044-1676-4 |oclc=478495}}{{Subscription required}}\n*{{cite book |last=Oberholtzer |first=Ellis Paxson|authorlink=Ellis Paxson Oberholtzer |title=A history of the United States since the Civil War |volume=2\u20133 |publisher=Macmillan|location=New York City |year=1922 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=3WYhAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&q |accessdate=April 12, 2010 |oclc=1535877 |isbn=0-8371-2642-8|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book |last=Olson |first=James C. |title=Red Cloud and the Sioux problem |publisher=University of Nebraska Press |location=[[Lincoln, Nebraska]] |year=1965 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/?id=qDTSt-tAm-gC&pg=PA103&dq=On+Monday+evening+the+Indians+were+all+taken+to+the+White+House&cd=1#v=onepage&q=On%20Monday%20evening%20the%20Indians%20were%20all%20taken%20to%20the%20White%20House |accessdate=April 3, 2010 |page=103 |chapter=Chapter 7: Red Cloud Visits the Great White Father |oclc=728240 | isbn=978-0-8032-5817-4|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite news |last=Pierson |first=Arthur Tappen |title=Zachariah Chandler: An Outline Sketch of his Life and Public Services |newspaper=Detroit Post and Tribune|pages=343\u2013345|year=1880 |oclc=300744189}}\n*{{cite book|last=Prucha |first=Francis Paul |authorlink=Francis Paul Prucha |title=The Great Father: The United States Government and the American Indians |publisher=University of Nebraska Press |location=Lincoln, Nebra